data.description: Fall in love with this traditional style home that has been completely updated & additional living space added. Former exterior patio converted to a Primary Bedroom (~222 SF) & 1-car garage converted to a Primary Bathroom & Closet (~276 SF) making this home 4 Bdr, 3 ba and ~1,869 SF. All hard surface flooring (no carpet), new interior and exterior paint, new fence, updated Bath 2, updated electric panel, new centralized A/C plus new wall unit for room addition. Open kitchen that has been completely remodeled w/ granite countertops, cabinets, sink, backsplash, stainless steel slide-in range, dishwasher, vent hood & wine cooler! Enjoy the cul-de-sac location w/ beautiful mature oak trees, covered patio, & spacious storage shed. Walking distance to Elementary & High Schools & quick access to Loop 410, the airport, North Star Mall, Quarry Market and the Broadway corridor. Don't miss the opportunity to submit an offer, it will not last!
